  {
    "arguments": {
        "shared-networks": [
            { "name": "floor1" },
            { "name": "office" }
        ]
    },
    "result": 0,
    "text": "2 IPv4 network(s) found"
}
Result is an integer representation of the status. Currently supported statuses are:


0 - success

1 - error

